	<p id="recipe_testimony_quote">I remember the first time I tasted a Rice Krispie Treat.  I was about five and was eating a bowl of rice krispies, while I was reading the box.  And then I noticed an ad on the box for a little plastic yellow thing with a long piece and a handle.  It was for putting the rice krispie treat on without getting your hands sticky!!!!  I was so excited I saved the UPS cards until I had enough to send away for it.  And the day it arrived my mom and I mad a batch of rice krispie treats!!!  </p>
<p><strong>Paige, NC</strong></p>
<p class="timestamp">Posted: 07-19-2009, 2:44 PM</p>
</div>

