<div id="print_whyuse">
<img src="/images/print_whyuse.jpg" width="196" height="249" alt="" />
<h2>Why use <em>Kellogg's&reg; Rice Krispies&reg;</em>?</h2>
<p>As the first crisped rice cereal, <em>Kellogg's&reg; Rice Krispies&reg;</em> has been bringing families together in the kitchen for nearly 80 years. The "cereal that talks" captivates adults and children alike, and the classic taste has become one of life's simple pleasures. To experience the timeless flavor, make your <em>Rice Krispies Treats&reg;</em> with the original <em>Rice Krispies&reg;</em> brand cereal.
</p>
</div>
